formance to, instead of focusing PR by PR on improvements, let's just look at how to use it and the benefits it brings.", markup='', info='', meta={}, block=True, hidden=False), Token(type='paragraph_close', tag='p', nesting=-1, attrs={}, map=None, level=0, children=None, content='', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=True, hidden=False), Token(type='paragraph_open', tag='p', nesting=1, attrs={}, map=[3506, 3507], level=0, children=None, content='', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=True, hidden=False), Token(type='inline', tag='', nesting=0, attrs={}, map=[3506, 3507], level=1, children=[Token(type='text', tag='', nesting=0, attrs={}, map=None, level=0, children=None, content="Today, Native AOT is focused on console applications, so let's create a console app:", markup='', info='', meta={}, block=False, hidden=False)], content="Today, Native AOT is focused on console applications, so let's create a console app:", markup='', info='', meta={}, block=True, hidden=False), Token(type='paragraph_close', tag='p', nesting=-1, attrs={}, map=None, level=0, children=None, content='', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=True, hidden=False), Token(type='fence', tag='code', nesting=0, attrs={}, map=[3508, 3511], level=0, children=None, content='dotnet new console -o nativeaotexample\n', markup='```', info='', meta={}, block=True, hidden=False), Token(type='paragraph_open', tag='p', nesting=1, attrs={}, map=[3512, 3513], level=0, children=None, content='', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=True, hidden=False), Token(type='inline', tag='', nesting=0, attrs={}, map=[3512, 3513], level=1, children=[Token(type='text', tag='', nesting=0, attrs={}, map=None, level=0, children=None, content='We now have our nativeaotexample directory containing a nativeaotexample.csproj and a "hello, world" Program.cs. To enable publishing the application with Native AOT, edit the .csproj to include this in the existing ', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=False, hidden=False), Token(type='html_inline