://github.com/huoyaoyuan'}, map=None, level=0, children=None, content='', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=False, hidden=False), Token(type='text', tag='', nesting=0, attrs={}, map=None, level=1, children=None, content='@huoyaoyuan', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=False, hidden=False), Token(type='link_close', tag='a', nesting=-1, attrs={}, map=None, level=0, children=None, content='', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=False, hidden=False), Token(type='text', tag='', nesting=0, attrs={}, map=None, level=0, children=None, content=' rewrote several delegate-related "FCalls" from being implemented in native code to instead being managed, resulting in less overhead when invoking these operations that are commonly involved in scenarios involving Marshal.GetDelegateForFunctionPointer. ', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=False, hidden=False), Token(type='link_open', tag='a', nesting=1, attrs={'href': 'https://github.com/dotnet/runtime/pull/68694'}, map=None, level=0, children=None, content='', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=False, hidden=False), Token(type='text', tag='', nesting=0, attrs={}, map=None, level=1, children=None, content='dotnet/runtime#68694', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=False, hidden=False), Token(type='link_close', tag='a', nesting=-1, attrs={}, map=None, level=0, children=None, content='', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=False, hidden=False), Token(type='text', tag='', nesting=0, attrs={}, map=None, level=0, children=None, content=' also moved some trivial functionality from native to managed, as part of relaxing argument validation on the use of pinning handles. This in turn measurably reduced the overhead involved with using GCHandle.Alloc for such pinning handles:', markup='', info='', meta={}, block=False, hidden=False)], content='Other PRs also accrued to improved interop performance. [dotnet/runtime#70000](https://github.com/dotnet/runtime/pull/70000) from [@huoyaoyuan](https://github.com/huoyaoyuan) rewrote several delegate-re